* {{rhymes|eɪʃən|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The [[weaning]] of a child from the breast, or of young [[animal]]s from their dam. {{defdate|First attested from around (1350 to 1470).}}<ref name=SOED>{{R:SOED5|page=5}}</ref>
